(6, 'CDR', 'Call Detail Recording. A stored database record\r\ncontaining data about a specific call. Processed as a unit\r\nand used to create billing records, a CDR contains details\r\nsuch as the called and calling parties, originating switch,\r\nterminating switch, call length, and time of day.'),
