(491, 115, 'SECOND ROUND:\r\nHow would we go about changing the rules of the report? \r\n\r\nWe need it to display records that do not have the primary contact name &amp; at least 1 of the other fields filled out in the primary contact section (Primary Phone, Primary Emergency Phone, Primary Emergency Email, or Site Email). \r\nContact Notes should not be a required field or considered in the rules. \r\n\r\nWe would not want to see sites in the data set that have a Primary Contact name and 1 of the fields filled out - Primary Phone, Primary Emergency Phone, Primary Emergency Email, or Site Email. Those would not be considered an exception that needs attention. \r\n\r\nThe report is showing data that we do not need to review.\r\n\r\nNEED TO SEE:\r\nif( primary contact name = nil){\r\nreport \r\n\r\n} else if( none of these has data[Primary Phone, Primary Emergency Phone, Primary Emergency Email, or Site Email] ){\r\nreport\r\n}\r\nDO NOT NEED TO SEE:'),
